# Man pages

## Tips about man pages

###  Invoke man pages of man page

```
$ man man
```

### Create manual pages index and Check for man pages available

```
$ sudo mandb
$ man -k passwd
```


### Invoke different man level - for files and configurations
```
$ man 5 crontab
```

### Invoke passwd manual page
```
$ man passwd
```

### How to to no clean the screen when we exit from the manual page

```
$ export LESS='-X'
```

### Shortcuts on man pages

- Shift + G -> Go to the end of the man page
- g -> Go to the begining 
- d -> scroll down a page
- u -> srooll up a page
- /word -> to search word in the page
- ?word -> to search backwards in the page



